      <h2 id="canYouHelp">Can you help FreeCEN to thrive?</h2>
      <p>FreeCEN would not exist without the technical volunteers, transcribers, proofreaders, validators, coordinators, managers and other volunteers who have created and sustained the project for over two decades. If you are interested in joining them, please use the ‘volunteer’ link in the main menu to find out more about how you can help.</p> 
      <p>If you would like to support us in another way, we always welcome donations to pay for our necessary costs: there is a link in the footer of every page, including this one.</p>
